1
00:00:19,269 --> 00:00:25,713
<i>September 21, 1945. That was the night I died.</i>

2
00:00:56,039 --> 00:00:58,112
Damn tramps.

3
00:00:58,808 --> 00:01:00,137
Watch it!

4
00:01:01,277 --> 00:01:03,546
- Disgusting!
- Is he dead?

5
00:01:03,547 --> 00:01:05,781
<i>The Americans'll be arriving any day now.</i>

6
00:01:05,782 --> 00:01:08,822
<i>These bums are disgrace!</i>

7
00:01:18,128 --> 00:01:20,001
<i>Mama...!</i>

8
00:01:21,464 --> 00:01:25,927
<i>Tell me, what day is it?</i>

9
00:01:35,379 --> 00:01:37,850
<i>Setsuko...</i>

10
00:01:48,091 --> 00:01:49,794
Another one.

11
00:02:03,240 --> 00:02:08,315
- What is this stuff?
- Never mind that. Just dump it!

12
00:02:19,956 --> 00:02:22,525
This one's a goner, too.

13
00:02:24,526 --> 00:02:27,100
You can see it in their eyes.

14
00:03:36,202 --> 00:03:42,338
<i><font color=#00ff00>Grave of the Fireflies</font></i>

15
00:03:44,107 --> 00:03:46,237
<font color=#ff00ff>Production Designer &
Executive Producer</font> <font color=#FF551>RYOICHI SATO</font>

